        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Most if not all of the items with "innate" regen effects will stack with each other, but tht may not always be the case.  For example, the Dain Belt, RoF Robe and Spirit Wracked Cord all have regen (two of the same kind) but are innate and do stack.</P><P>Stacking problems generally start to arise with clickable effects that sit in the same tier.  For example, the 10th Ring and Fungi Staff will not stack.  Single buffs of these kind will stack with your innate effects though, which is very nice.</P><P>Savan<BR>Afterlife</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
