        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         As far as I know, innate (or worn) AoB items will stack to infinity, but it's entirely possible there's a limit such as that placed on FT, but I highly doubt it.</P><P>I currently have two innate AoB items that do indeed stack and I think there are 2-3 others that we as Int casters can wear.  There are also a few clickable AoB items, but these don't excite me much.</P><P>Seru now has an item with innate AoB2 on it (4 regen) and I'm hoping they'll add this effect to more caster gear in the future.</P><P>Savan<BR>Afterlife</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
